Structure.Surface Connections:
* The [[Belltower]] was rumored to have a trapdoor exit into the sewers.<ref>
* [[General Articles for All Needs]] had a hidden trapdoor into the sewers behind its counter.<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/Luck Takes a Vacation|8}}
* The [[Smoke Wyrm]] had a secret entrance into the sewers.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|2528}} 
